Subject: FEATURE: propagation of local assignments
Date: Thu, 22 Oct 2009 12:05:11 -0600
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.936)

Consider an assignment, x:=e on transition t.

If (not vacuous(t,x) and x in local(t) and
     (forall u in support(e) . u in lw(t)) and
     (forall t'' in (pre(pre(post(post(t)))) . AA(t'',x) = e and
      (forall u in (support(e) - {x}) . vacuous (t'',u)) then

	forall t' in post(post(t)
		replace(t',x,e) <-- replace all occurrences of x in RHS of  
assignments and enabling with e
	forall t'' in pre(pre(post(post(t)))
		AA(t'',x) := x


